snippet.title: Mission Improbable launch trailer
snippet.description:
The launch trailer for the Half-Life 2: Episode 2 mod "Mission Improbable"!

Please go to http://www.missionimprobable.org or http://www.moddb.com/mods/mission-improbable for more information and download links!

Music: "Requiem" by Proyect X (http://soundcloud.com/profesorproyect)
